data.title: TypeScript in the secure development
data.description: TypeScript is a typed superset of JavaScript that compiles to plain JavaScript. TypeScript is pure object oriented with classes, interfaces and statically typed like C# or Java. TypeScript is developed and maintained by Microsoft. It is open source and can be installed via npm. TypeScript is JavaScript
